OL,3,CPolice investigate arson attack on
OL,4,Chotel subject to anti-immigration
OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,FPolice are investigating an "extremely
OL,8,Fdangerous" arson attack on a hotel
OL,9,Fwhich has been subject to anti-
OL,10,Fimmigration protests.
OL,12,FOfficers from Hampshire Constabulary
OL,13,Fwere called after a flare was put
OL,14,Fthrough an open ground-floor window of
OL,15,Fthe Highfield House Hotel in
OL,16,FShaftesbury Avenue, Southampton, at
OL,17,Fabout 2.15am on Sunday 7 September.
