OL,7,FA force spokesperson said:
OL,8,F"Thankfully, the fire caused by the
OL,9,Fflare was quickly put out and nobody
OL,10,Fwas injured.
OL,12,F"Enquiries are under way to establish
OL,13,Fthe exact circumstances of the
OL,14,Fincident, including locating two
OL,15,Fpeople seen approaching the hotel and
OL,16,Fthen fleeing the scene.
OL,18,F"The two people left the area along
OL,19,FShaftesbury Avenue.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/8
