OL,7,F"One was wearing a dark hooded top and
OL,8,Fhad his face covered, and the other
OL,9,Fhad a white hooded top on."
OL,11,FThe hotel was subject to an anti-
OL,12,Fimmigration protest on September 1,
OL,13,Fwith a counter protest held by Stand
OL,14,FUp To Racism.
OL,16,FChief Inspector Chris Douglas said:
OL,17,F"Fortunately, this fire was quickly
OL,18,Fput out, but this was an extremely
OL,19,Fdangerous act and could have had fatal
OL,20,Fconsequences.
