OL,7,F"Our local neighbourhood policing team
OL,8,Fwill be carrying out additional
OL,9,Fpatrols in Portswood in the coming
OL,10,Fdays, and if anyone has any concerns
OL,11,Fthen please do speak to them.
OL,13,F"I want to urge anyone with
OL,14,Finformation, however small you think
OL,15,Fit may be, to get in touch and share
OL,16,Fthis with us.
