OL,7,F"If you have any CCTV which may have
OL,8,Fcaptured the two men either in the
OL,9,Fmoments leading up to or after the
OL,10,Fincident, then we would ask you to
OL,11,Fshare this with us.
OL,13,F"We are working closely with local
OL,14,Fauthorities as part of this
OL,15,Finvestigation."
OL,17,FThe force spokesperson declined to
OL,18,Fcomment on the use of the hotel but
OL,19,Fsaid: "It is being investigated as an
OL,20,Farson.
