OL,7,F"There is no link to other matters at
OL,8,Fthis time."
OL,10,FSouthampton Stand Up to Racism says it
OL,11,F"condemns in the strongest possible
OL,12,Fterms the arson attack on Highfield
OL,13,FHouse Hotel".
OL,15,FA spokesperson said: "Thankfully, the
OL,16,Ffire was contained and no one was
OL,17,Fhurt, but this remains an extremely
OL,18,Fworrying situation."
