OL,7,FSatvir Kaur MP for Southampton Test
OL,8,Fsaid: "This is horrific behaviour
OL,9,Fwhich is inexcusable.
OL,11,F"Southampton is a proud city of
OL,12,Fsanctuary, and actions like this will
OL,13,Fnot and should never define us.
OL,15,F"This type of sadistic targeting and
OL,16,Fendangerment of life doesn't just
OL,17,Fhappen in isolation, so I would urge
OL,18,Fthose that are promoting hate and
OL,19,Fdivision within our communities to
OL,20,Frealise words matter.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G7/8
