OL,5,Cprotests
OL,7,F"Seeing this escalation into dangerous
OL,8,Fcriminal behaviour is shocking and
OL,9,Fwon't be tolerated in our city.
OL,11,F"I strongly urge anyone with
OL,12,Finformation that can assist the police
OL,13,Fwith their ongoing investigation to
OL,14,Fcome forward.
OL,16,F"Everyone in our city deserves to feel
OL,17,Fsafe; I will be reaching out to
OL,18,FHampshire Constabulary and others on
OL,19,Fwhat more can be done to prevent
OL,20,Ffuture incidents like this."
